# Design Tokens — Car & Driver Marketplace

All tokens are CSS custom properties defined in `src/index.css` `:root`. Always use these variables — never hardcode hex values, pixel sizes, or font names.

## Colors

### Primary Brand
- `--color-blue-cobalt`: #1B5F8A (primary actions, links, CTAs)
- `--color-blue-cobalt-dark`: #154d70 (hover states)
- `--color-blue-cobalt-light`: #60A5FA (accents, highlights)
- `--color-blue-dark`: #154d70 (alias for cobalt-dark)

### Secondary
- `--color-red`: #D2232A (official C/D red — alerts, destructive)
- `--color-red-dark`: #b31f24

### Neutrals (use these, not raw hex)
- `--color-black`: #000000
- `--color-dark`: #222222 (headers, footers, primary text)
- `--color-gray-700`: #4a4a4a
- `--color-gray-600`: #666666
- `--color-gray-500`: #6b6b6b (WCAG AA on white)
- `--color-gray-300`: #cdcdcd
- `--color-gray-200`: #e5e5e5 (borders)
- `--color-gray-100`: #f5f5f5 (backgrounds)
- `--color-gray-50`: #fafafa
- `--color-white`: #ffffff

### Semantic
- `--color-success`: #26870D (+ `-dark`, `-light`, `-border`, `-50`)
- `--color-warning`: #f59e0b (+ `-dark`, `-light`)
- `--color-error`: #ef4444 (+ `-dark`, `-light`, `-50`)
- `--color-info`: #0288d1 (+ `-light`, `-border`)

### Special
- `--color-gold`: #DBCA8B / `--color-gold-light`: #FEF3C7 / `--color-gold-dark`: #A59143
- `--color-purple`: #7c3aed / `--color-purple-dark`: #6d28d9
- `--color-highlight`: #fef08a
- `--color-facebook`: #1877F2

### Dark Theme
- `--color-dark-bg`: #0a1628
- `--color-dark-surface`: #1a1a2e
- `--color-dark-surface-hover`: slightly lighter variant

### Gradients
- `--gradient-dark`, `--gradient-dark-alt`, `--gradient-blue`
- `--gradient-success`, `--gradient-light`, `--gradient-blue-light`

## Typography

### Font Stacks
- `--font-sans`: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif
- `--font-serif`: 'Lora', Georgia, serif
- `--font-condensed`: 'Barlow Condensed', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif

### Semantic Font Aliases (use these)
- `--font-heading`: var(--font-sans) — all headings, labels, buttons
- `--font-body`: var(--font-sans) — body text, descriptions
- `--font-article`: var(--font-serif) — editorial/article content
- `--font-label`: var(--font-condensed) — labels, badges, tags
- `--font-display`: var(--font-sans)

### Font Weights
- `--font-weight-regular`: 400
- `--font-weight-medium`: 500
- `--font-weight-semibold`: 600
- `--font-weight-bold`: 700
- `--font-weight-extrabold`: 800
- `--font-weight-black`: 900

### Font Sizes
- `--font-size-2xs`: 10px | `--font-size-xs`: 12px | `--font-size-sm`: 14px
- `--font-size-base` / `--font-size-md`: 16px
- `--font-size-lg`: 18px | `--font-size-xl`: 20px | `--font-size-2xl`: 24px
- `--font-size-3xl`: 30px | `--font-size-4xl`: 36px | `--font-size-5xl`: 48px
- `--font-size-6xl`: 60px | `--font-size-7xl`: 72px
- Semantic: `--font-size-caption`, `--font-size-body`, `--font-size-subtitle`, `--font-size-title`, `--font-size-display`, `--font-size-display-lg`

### Line Heights
- `--line-height-none`: 1 | `--line-height-tight`: 1.15
- `--line-height-snug`: 1.25 | `--line-height-normal`: 1.5
- `--line-height-relaxed`: 1.625 | `--line-height-loose`: 2

## Spacing (4px base with half steps)

- `--spacing-0`: 0 | `--spacing-px`: 1px | `--spacing-0-5`: 2px
- `--spacing-1`: 4px | `--spacing-1-5`: 6px | `--spacing-2`: 8px
- `--spacing-2-5`: 10px | `--spacing-3`: 12px | `--spacing-3-5`: 14px
- `--spacing-4`: 16px | `--spacing-5`: 20px | `--spacing-6`: 24px
- `--spacing-7`: 28px | `--spacing-8`: 32px | `--spacing-9`: 36px
- `--spacing-10`: 40px | `--spacing-12`: 48px | `--spacing-14`: 56px
- `--spacing-16`: 64px | `--spacing-20`: 80px | `--spacing-24`: 96px
- `--spacing-28`: 112px | `--spacing-32`: 128px

## Layout
- `--max-width-container`: 1280px
- `--max-width-content`: 1280px
- `--max-width-narrow`: 960px
- `--content-padding`: var(--spacing-8)
- `--header-height`: 46px
- `--subnav-height`: 50px

## Border Radius
- `--border-radius-sm`: 4px (inputs, small buttons)
- `--border-radius-md`: 6px (cards, dropdowns)
- `--border-radius-lg`: 8px (modals, large cards)
- `--border-radius-xl`: 12px (hero cards)
- `--border-radius-2xl`: 16px (feature cards)
- `--border-radius-full`: 9999px (avatars, badges, pills)

## Shadows
- `--shadow-sm`: 0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.05)
- `--shadow-md`: 0 3px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.08)
- `--shadow-lg`: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.12)
- `--shadow-xl`: 0 16px 48px rgba(0,0,0,0.16)

## Transitions
- `--transition-fast`: 150ms ease (hovers, toggles)
- `--transition-normal`: 200ms ease (default)
- `--transition-slow`: 300ms ease (modals, complex animations)

## Breakpoints (no CSS variables — hardcoded)
- Mobile: max-width 480px
- Tablet: max-width 768px
- Desktop small: max-width 1024px
- Desktop: max-width 1200px
- Wide: min-width 1401px
